# Constants & Config

Never hardcode routes, labels, API URLs, asset paths, or error messages.

- Routes → `lib/constants/routes.ts`
- API paths → `lib/constants/api-endpoints.ts`
- Copy/labels → `lib/constants/content.ts`
- Assets → `lib/constants/assets.ts`
- Env vars → `lib/config/env.ts` (use `NEXT_PUBLIC_*` only for browser-safe values)
